result.name: Beijing Crepes

reviews.text: I grow up with this in Beijing. Times have changed … for the better! The recipe is tuned and variety added, it maintained a theme of being Chinese yet new and I would describe the new ones are better than the original. There was another similar attempt a few years ago near Wellington St., But they folded, I hope this one is here to stay.
It was a French and Turkish way to present nice short Delicious quick crepes in Chinese way. Good but no way to seat for five minutes to enjoy your crepe. Ok good continuation
Delicious! Such a great find! Fantastic price!! We recommend the spicy chicken, duck and satay pork!!

Beijing origin crepe like simple snack. On a basic thin crepe, you may choose many different type toppings from sweet banana to Beijing duck. It is also offered set menu with drunks. There is no seat. You order and pick up only. Since it is prepared on your order, it takes some time.
Very good food

result.name: 煎餅廚房

reviews.text: 價錢上可接受， ok好食又飽肚，絕對係下午茶之選。
食物－般 ，但又係一間飢餓式嘅營銷煎餅店， 四五十蚊買舊煎餅但係大概等半個鐘到啦。 想轉下口味嘅朋友仔都可以試下嘅！
小菜不錯不貴可以品嘗。
